description: Discover this spacious 2-bed, 2-bath condo on Southie’s desirable East Side! Built in 2013, this 1,259 SF home feat. covered GARAGE parking, on-site storage, and private outdoor space. Its open-concept layout enhances the already generous living area, ideal for entertaining. The well-appointed living room boasts a gas FP with direct access to an oversized, private deck spanning the entire length of the unit, perfect for year-round enjoyment. The gourmet kitchen includes SS appliances, granite countertops, ample storage, and a large island. The primary bedroom offers a peaceful retreat with an ensuite bath and custom walk-in closet, while the second bedroom works well as an office, nursery, or guest room. Additional highlights include HW flooring, Central AC, surround sound, 10-foot ceilings, and IN-UNIT laundry. Just minutes from East Broadway’s restaurants and shops, Seaport, Castle Island, beaches, public transit, and with easy access to I-93/Mass Pike - this unit is a must see!
